    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Besiege colossal creatures, plead for the favor of the gods, and forge your destiny in the tech tree. Equip units with unique items, build, recruit, and survive waves of enemies in a solo or co-op experience that fuses RTS and roguelike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roguelike:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In every battle, you can invoke the favor of the gods to add unique strategies to the combat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To obtain it, you must collect enough souls; their origin is a mystery, and although there are clues scattered throughout the world, no one knows their source yet.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330110/extras/43c6d0de9610a557e9f204f28c27e388.poster.avif?t=1771872402\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330110/extras/43c6d0de9610a557e9f204f28c27e388.webm?t=1771872402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330110/extras/43c6d0de9610a557e9f204f28c27e388.mp4?t=1771872402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tech Tree:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After each battle, you can choose upgrades for your empire through various branches, each with its own strategy. This will allow you to grow stronger to face increasingly powerful enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330110/extras/955a5ca56daa69a540cc866f5aec8bb2.poster.avif?t=1771872402\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330110/extras/955a5ca56daa69a540cc866f5aec8bb2.webm?t=1771872402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330110/extras/955a5ca56daa69a540cc866f5aec8bb2.mp4?t=1771872402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Equip your units:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obtain items in combat, explore hidden locations on the map, or complete special challenges to acquire them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These items will improve the stats of the unit that carries them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330110/extras/c68aa4108d663d144acec7ef3fbadec1.poster.avif?t=1771872402\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330110/extras/c68aa4108d663d144acec7ef3fbadec1.webm?t=1771872402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330110/extras/c68aa4108d663d144acec7ef3fbadec1.mp4?t=1771872402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Faithful to classic RTS:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master micro and macro management, build strategic bases, and gather essential resources.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy co-op or custom matches to face friends and rivals.</p></li></ul>",
